## Event Schemas (exact — registered at `KernelBootstrap.__init__`)

| Event Type | Required Payload Keys | Registered Version |
|---|---|---|
| `agent.registered` | `agent_id: str`, `role: str`, `capabilities: List[str]` | `"1.0"` |
| `agent.unregistered` | `agent_id: str` | `"1.0"` |
| `agent.task_submitted` | `task_id: str`, `agent_id: str`, `instruction: str`, `constraints: dict`, `correlation_id: str` | `"1.0"` |
| `agent.task_completed` | `task_id: str`, `steps_taken: int`, `output: str`, `correlation_id: str` | `"1.0"` |
| `agent.task_failed` | `task_id: str`, `reason: str`, `step_at_failure: int`, `correlation_id: str` | `"1.0"` |
| `improvement.patch_proposed` | `patch_id: str`, `target_module: str`, `proposed_by: str` | `"1.0"` |
| `improvement.patch_approved` | `patch_id: str`, `approver_id: str` | `"1.0"` |
| `improvement.patch_applied` | `patch_id: str`, `module_name: str`, `new_version: str` | `"1.0"` |
| `improvement.patch_rejected` | `patch_id: str`, `reason: str` | `"1.0"` |

